.SH NAME
drm_client_modeset_dpms \- Set DPMS mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" drm_client_modeset_dpms
.BI "(struct drm_client_dev *client "  ","
.BI "int mode "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "client" 12
DRM client
.IP "mode" 12
DPMS mode
.SH "NOTE"
For atomic drivers \fImode\fP is reduced to on/off.
.SH "RETURN"
Zero on success or negative error code on failure.
